OL,3,CWaste crime operation aims to stop fly-
OL,4,Ctipping in countryside
OL,6,FPolice have been carrying out a waste
OL,7,Fcrime operation in rural Hampshire to
OL,8,Fintercept criminals on the road and
OL,9,Fprevent potential fly-tipping.
OL,11,FThirty drivers were stopped by
OL,12,Fofficers at Blackbushe Airport off the
OL,13,FA30 near Yateley as part of the sting
OL,14,Fon Thursday.
OL,16,FIn one case, the Environment Agency
OL,17,Fdealt with a waste carrier who was
OL,18,Funable to provide evidence of their
OL,19,Fwaste carrier's licence or waste
OL,20,Ftransfer note.
