OL,3,CWaste crime operation aims to stop fly-
OL,4,Ctipping in countryside
OL,6,FThe main focus was those transporting
OL,7,Frubbish, however vehicles carrying
OL,8,Fother goods and machinery were also
OL,9,Fstopped and checked.
OL,11,FPolice say the majority were
OL,12,Froadworthy and in order, however, a
OL,13,Fnumber of issues were identified.
OL,15,FTwo vehicles were being driven with
OL,16,Fcracked windscreens, three drivers
OL,17,Fwere ticketed due to their loaded
OL,18,Fvehicles being overweight, one driver
OL,19,Fwas given a ticket for driving without
OL,20,Fa number plate.
