OL,3,CWaste crime operation aims to stop fly-
OL,4,Ctipping in countryside
OL,6,FOther drivers were found with issues
OL,7,Fincluding defective tyres, and driving
OL,8,Fwithout tax and a pickup truck was
OL,9,Fseized for having no insurance.
OL,11,FPC Terry Read, who ran the operation,
OL,12,Fsaid: "Operations like this provide a
OL,13,Fgreat opportunity for police teams to
OL,14,Fpool their skills together, and also
OL,15,Fcall upon the expertise of partner
OL,16,Fagencies to target offenders using the
OL,17,Fcounty's roads.
