OL,3,CWaste crime operation aims to stop fly-
OL,4,Ctipping in countryside
OL,6,F"Our focus was on rural criminality,
OL,7,Fincluding fly-tipping which blights
OL,8,Four countryside, and we had the
OL,9,FEnvironment Agency and local authority
OL,10,Fwith us to support this work.
OL,12,F"Roads policing officers were working
OL,13,Fthrough the morning to identify
OL,14,Fvehicles of interest.
OL,16,F"Waste carrier licences were checked,
OL,17,Fand police teams and other agencies
OL,18,Fincluding DVSA and HMRC conducted
OL,19,Fadditional checks and enquiries to
OL,20,Fdeal with any further offences
OL,21,Fidentified.
