OL,3,CWaste crime operation aims to stop fly-
OL,4,Ctipping in countryside
OL,6,F"A huge part of our county is rural,
OL,7,Fand we want the communities in these
OL,8,Fareas to feel supported, to know that
OL,9,Fwe are out there being proactive, and
OL,10,Fwe encourage them to keep reporting
OL,11,Fconcerns around rural crime and
OL,12,Fsuspicious people or vehicles to
OL,13,Fpolice."
OL,15,FHart Neighbourhoods Policing Team led
OL,16,Fthe operation, with support from
OL,17,Fofficers within Roads Policing, the
OL,18,FCountry Watch Rural Crime Task Force,
OL,19,Fand the Northern Neighbourhood
OL,20,FEnforcement Team.
