OL,4,Ctipping in countryside
OL,6,FHart District Council, the Environment
OL,7,FAgency, DVSA, HMRC, and the Motor
OL,8,FInsurers' Bureau were also involved in
OL,9,Fthe operation.
OL,11,FPolice & Crime Commissioner Donna
OL,12,FJones said: "Operations like this show
OL,13,Fthe importance of partnership working
OL,14,Fto help crack down on fly-tipping and
OL,15,Fcriminality across our rural areas.
OL,17,F"This proactive approach offers
OL,18,Freassurance that police are listening
OL,19,Fto the concerns of our rural
OL,20,Fcommunities and acting on them."
